Package com.netflix.genie.common.messages

Classes that represent request/responses to/from Genie services

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseRequest
    Base class to capture common request functionality.
    BaseResponse
    Base class to capture common response functionality.
    ClusterConfigRequest
    Represents request to the ClusterConfig REST resource.
    ClusterConfigResponse
    Represents response from the ClusterConfig REST resource.
    HiveConfigRequest
    Represents request to the Hive Config REST resource.
    HiveConfigResponse
    Represents response from the Hive Config REST resource.
    JobInfoRequest
    Represents request to the Jobs REST resource.
    JobInfoResponse
    Represents the response from the Jobs REST resource.
    JobStatusResponse
    Represents a response from the Jobs REST resource, including only the status.
    PigConfigRequest
    Represents request to the Pig Config REST resource.
    PigConfigResponse
    Represents response from the PigConfig REST resource.
